SQL_STMT_U.val: select A.CO_ID ,A.ACCOUNT_NO, A.F_HD, A.ACCOUNT_NAME, A.LEVEL_NO, A.F_NORMAL, A.CURR_ID, A.ACCGRP, B.ACCOUNT_NO, B.COST_CENTER, B.BEGINNING_AMT, B.ENDING_01, B.ENDING_02, B.ENDING_03, B.ENDING_04, B.ENDING_05, B.ENDING_06, B.ENDING_07, B.ENDING_08, B.ENDING_09, B.ENDING_10, B.ENDING_11, B.ENDING_12, B.ENDING_13, B.DB_01, B.DB_02, B.DB_03, B.DB_04, B.DB_05, B.DB_06, B.DB_07, B.DB_08, B.DB_09, B.DB_10, B.DB_11, B.DB_12, B.DB_13, B.CR_01, B.CR_02, B.CR_03, B.CR_04, B.CR_05, B.CR_06, B.CR_07, B.CR_08, B.CR_09, B.CR_10, B.CR_11, B.CR_12, B.CR_13 from GL_ACCOUNT a (nolock) LEFT join GL_BALANCE b(nolock) on a.co_id = b.co_id and a.ACCOUNT_NO = b.ACCOUNT_NO AND B.BR_ID = ':3' AND B.CURR_ID = ':6' AND B.FISCAL_YEAR = :4 WHERE a.CO_ID = ':1' and a.F_HD = ':2' :5 order by B.ACCOUNT_NO, B.COST_CENTER

Text.valUnicode: T R I A L B A L A N C E

ExpSyntax.val: IF(({1,61}='' OR {1,61} = NULL()) AND ({1,64}='' OR {1,64} = NULL()), '', 'AND a.account_no BETWEEN'&ASCIIChr(39)&Trim({1,61})&ASCIIChr(39)&'AND'&ASCIIChr(39)&Trim({1,64})&ASCIIChr(39) )
